    GitHub mid-install.

    The 7 screenshots are copied from samples/.../docs/screenshots/ to
    wwwroot/img/woocommerce/ — kept in sync via the same capture.mjs run.
    Versioned ?v=… on each src so a re-capture busts the browser cache
    without a page-version bump.
*@

@{
