                <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 mb-2 px-1">WooCommerce install</p>
                <nav class="flex flex-col text-sm">
                    <a href="/docs/woocommerce#before"   class="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-dgb-900 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 no-underline">Before you start</a>
                    <a href="/docs/woocommerce#zip"      class="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-dgb-900 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 no-underline">1. Get the ZIP</a>
                    <a href="/docs/woocommerce#upload"   class="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-dgb-900 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 no-underline">2. Upload + activate</a>
                    <a href="/docs/woocommerce#account"  class="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-dgb-900 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 no-underline">3. Register a merchant</a>
                    <a href="/docs/woocommerce#configure" class="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-dgb-900 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 no-underline">4. Configure the plugin</a>
