                        <a href="https://github.com/DennisPitallano/digibyte-wallet/tree/main/samples/woocommerce-plugin" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-dgb-500 no-underline">Plugin source on GitHub ↗</a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/DennisPitallano/digibyte-wallet/blob/main/samples/woocommerce-plugin/docs/customer-flow.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-dgb-500 no-underline">Customer flow ↗</a>
                    </div>
